text:
This extension allows you to use [academicons](https://jpswalsh.github.io/academicons/) in your Quarto HTML documents. It provides an `{{&lt; ai &gt;}}` shortcode:
- Mandatory `&lt;icon-name&gt;`:
``` markdown
{{&lt; ai &lt;
google-scholar 
&gt; &gt;}}
```
- Optional `&lt;size=…&gt;`:
``` markdown
{{&lt; ai &lt;
google-scholar 
&gt; &lt;size=…&gt; &gt;}}
```
- Optional `&lt;color=…&gt;`:
``` markdown
{{&lt; ai &lt;
google-scholar 
&gt; &lt;color=…&gt; &gt;}}
```
